# {{ project_name }}

An Astra AI Server generated by `astra-cli`.

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
pip install -e .

# Run development server
astra dev

# Or with uvicorn directly
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

## API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/health` | Health check |
| GET | `/ready` | Readiness check |
| GET | `/v1/agents` | List agents |
| GET | `/v1/agents/{id}` | Get agent info |
| POST | `/v1/agents/{id}/generate` | Generate response |
| POST | `/v1/agents/{id}/stream` | Stream response (SSE) |

## Configuration

Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and configure:

```bash
cp .env.example .env
```

## Adding Agents

Create a new agent in `app/agents/`:

```python
from astra import Agent, Gemini

my_agent = Agent(
    name="my-agent",
    model=Gemini("gemini-1.5-flash"),
    instructions="You are a helpful assistant.",
)
```

Then register it in `app/agents/__init__.py`:

```python
from app.agents.my_agent import my_agent
register_agent(my_agent)
```

## Adding Features

```bash
astra add rate-limit
astra add observability-otel
astra add ui
```

